Subinterfaces of PlanElement in org.cougaar.planning.ldm.plan
 interface Aggregation
          Aggregation Interface An Aggregation is a kind of PlanElement that merges multiple tasks into a single task.
 interface Allocation
          Allocation Interface An Allocation is a type of PlanElement which represents the Asset that will complete the Task.
 interface AllocationforCollections
          AllocationforCollections Interface -- represents setter methods for the RemoteAllocationLP and the RescindLP to keep track of what tasks were to sent out.
 interface AssetTransfer
          AssetTransfer Interface An AssetTransfer is a type of PlanElement which represents an Asset being assigned to another Agent for use.
 interface Disposition
          A PlanElement which represents an end-state disposition of a task.
 interface Expansion
          Expansion Interface An Expansion is a kind of PlanElement that represents a Workflow that is the result of an expansion of a Task.
 interface NewExpansion
          NewExpansion Interface Allows access to the single sub-task's allocation result information used to aggregate this Expansion's latest reported allocationresult
 interface NewPlanElement
          NewPlanElement Interface provides setter methods to build a PlanElement object
 interface PEforCollections
          PEforCollections Interface -- represents setter methods for the NotificationLP to set the Reported Result for PlanElements
 interface PlanElementForAssessor
          Special Interface to PlanElement for Assessors only.
